    "description": "You start as 1 single pixel, But that's no fun! As you progress, the game evolves into a 2d side-scrolling action advenuture! Scroll down to learn all about it!<br><br><i>By the way, if you prefer to jump in a game without spoilers, I have prepared a spoiler free teaser trailer just for you! Both trailers are found above.</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/5e4e7a491354b4f399f71a2ac4a3f785.avif?t=1655471290\" width=616 height=142 /></span><br><strong>START:</strong><br>A game where you truly start from the bottom, you begin the game as the smallest fragment of a video-game character, you are Juan, a single pixel! You have never known anything else except, as Juan would put it, the &quot;frikkin pixel life&quot;!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/80d4de2e9ec036f44133f8aea382507d.poster.avif?t=1655471290\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/80d4de2e9ec036f44133f8aea382507d.webm?t=1655471290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>GROW:</strong><br>As you play, and level up your abilities, you get to see the game practically build itself up from something simple and unimpressive, to an immersive action platformer! You will be surprised by how much the game has changed by the end!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/45d9a8b101ff8028bd53386844944226.poster.avif?t=1655471290\" width=616 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/45d9a8b101ff8028bd53386844944226.webm?t=1655471290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/45d9a8b101ff8028bd53386844944226.mp4?t=1655471290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>UPGRADES:</strong><br>Like any good game, there will be lots of upgrades! Unique enhancers that help you with you defeat enemies, and upgrades that will take you far beyond.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/ae7fa10740b1689500f6261eb7abbf7f.poster.avif?t=1655471290\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/ae7fa10740b1689500f6261eb7abbf7f.webm?t=1655471290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/ae7fa10740b1689500f6261eb7abbf7f.mp4?t=1655471290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>GET STRONGER:</strong><br>As you DESTROY your foes you will, of-course, get stronger... Level up! Invest Stats! Get bigger! Get better! Be the very best pixely dude you can be!<br><br><br>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/52ac8be7ae4dbd40beddb6dd79ff0100.webp?t=1655471290\" width=239 height=46 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Battle your way through unique enemies, and level up along the way, becoming more powerful to stand up to the evolving threats around you!<br></li><li>Invest your stat points to suit your play style, and access new ways to spend them as you level up!<br></li><li>Immerse in comedic story-telling conversations as you discover new ways to upgrade your gear!<br></li><li>Unlock new game mechanics as you discover the retro pixel-graphic style world ahead of you!<br></li><li>Engage in Hack-N-Slash style combat as you develop newer ways of fighting enemies such as getting an arm to punch or a sword to SLISHY SLASH with!<br></li><li>Replay Value features, get more out of your game with features like the Battle Arena, End-Game Prestige and Mushroom-Smith Upgrades!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763160/extras/05c9a15ff2facfcfb7a8a446f28bf39d.webp?t=1655471290\" width=155 height=56 /></span><br>A quirky and lighthearted story, which tends to break the rules of the usual game’s story telling dialect. You will find Juan to be a little more aware of the nature of his existence than the average video-game character…<br><br>It’s unconventional, it’s comedic, and you just kinda gotta try it to see what I mean.",
